{"tid":1694426,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"3年級仔數學功課教極唔識湖北36歲母親激到心肌梗塞","createTime":"2019-11-05T07:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T07:33:48.000Z","uid":236171,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"60f455671c341138cfafad1d6562e3953ed49876","tid":1694426,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>內地一名36歲媽媽早前因就讀小學三年級的兒子，做數學功課時「教極唔識」，氣得呼吸困難、心臟不適需要送院，經檢查後證實因情緒誘發心肌梗塞。</strong><br />\n<br />\n事發上周五（1日），湖北36歲王女士在家，教導就讀小學3年級兒子做功課，其間兒子做數學功課時竟然一題也答不對，無論她如何解釋仍是不懂，「我講了好多遍，他依然不懂，我氣得要炸了」。<br />\n<br />\n王女士教訓兒子後，突然感覺心慌胸悶，呼吸困難，「我趕緊打電話給我老公，請老公趕快載我到醫院」。入院診治後，醫生證實王女士因情緒激動誘發心肌梗塞，指她送院時已感到胸悶，大汗淋漓，幸好有及時送院急救，否則或會有猝死風險。<br />\n<br />\n王女士事後表示，過去一年常常因兒子的功課問題發脾氣，沒料會遇上如此嚴重的情況，她目前仍在醫院接受治療。"},{"pid":"05ce74cb9be15848132dd3c5fb3eca98608fa747","tid":1694426,"uid":236171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:10:19.000Z","msg":"激死你阿媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a9832caf1f679d7acb4b828f1e9e3ae470bbee","tid":1694426,"uid":318362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:14:11.000Z","msg":"真係激死"},{"pid":"e0df26550f8ccc7c9e004872bdce58a1f2b3ccd0","tid":1694426,"uid":76913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:14:32.000Z","msg":"醫學一早說明左遺傳基因既重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5925831682ee4014236f76dc868485a24ea75c0c","tid":1694426,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http